{{see|Jill}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From [[Jill]], a variant of the proper name [[Gill]], itself a female form either of [[Julius]] (then also Gillian) or of [[Aegidius]].

===Noun===
'''jill'''

# A young [[woman]]; a [[sweetheart]].

